description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a motivated individual to join our busy &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Facilities team (Hotel Services) in the delivery of a continuously improving safe, high quality service to patients, staff and visitors.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;To coordinate services, predominantly Catering and Domestic, based at Wathwood Hospital, and to work with the wider Facilities Department.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Experience in a supervisory or junior management position within a similar environment is essential though not necessarily within the NHS.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our DBS check is free, you have no fees to pay!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSteve BradshawJob titleFacilities Operational Manager (North)Email addresssteven.bradshaw@nottshc.nhs.ukTelephone number01777 247479Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gary Thompson, Facilities Support Services Manager (North)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01777 247479&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively contact Clare Saville on 01777 247788 who will put you in touch with a relevant manager.&lt;/p&gt;
